{"type": "article", "id": 31084, "title": "他打造的灯具想把光“盛”起来｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-08-16T23:04:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 31583, "name": "Sonic Architect"}, {"id": 31584, "name": "Estudio Pum"}, {"id": 31585, "name": "Producks"}, {"id": 31586, "name": "Jaipur Rugs"}, {"id": 31539, "name": "Pavel Vetrov"}, {"id": 31587, "name": "Martín Azúa"}, {"id": 31588, "name": "Paula Blankenship"}, {"id": 31589, "name": "Sahil Thappa"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 125, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016081623392489fV0r5xpPdujH7U.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Light Container by Martín Azúa</h3><p>西班牙设计师 <a href=\"http://www.martinazua.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Martín Azúa</a> 在自己的设计作品 Numbered 系列中通过这些名为 Light Container 的吊灯大胆地表达了自己对光的想象：假如光线有自己的形体和重量的话，灯具会是什么样？Light Container 的灯罩由黑色铁丝构成，就像是篮子一样将洁白的椭圆形灯包裹起来，有一种独特的悬浮感。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.martinazua.com/product/light-container/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价从 380 欧元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233727o392vk54GiUbgtCf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761719\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233727THB4ZC1sKfQVwPgW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608162337280yqg9rKjis8tIbEx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.803711\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233727lbmfhBzcXC1kKe4I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.507216\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233728DAOxjdGEUaJpSyz0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.360352\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233727IhN9lfHDZcUvPLpj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.531959\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>NodPod by Paula Blankenship</h3><p>旅行时难免会有犯困的时候，但是想要舒服地打个盹并不是一件容易的事情，虽然 U 型枕解决了一部分问题，但避免不了颈椎因为身体前倾而受到的压力。室内设计师 Paula Blankenship 在经过多年的研发之后推出了这款能够保护颈椎的下巴枕 <a href=\"http://www.thenodpod.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">NodPod</a>，它的表面由防水面料制成，内部则填充了柔软舒适的记忆海绵，不会给人造成紧绷感。使用时只要将 NodPod 固定在椅背上，用它托住下巴即可。如果你对这个新奇的枕头感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1474114988/the-ultimate-sleep-travel-solution-nodpod\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 30 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233755QzHmYG7kBTFsU214.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.402941\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233756aMuzbNBy7Fxg2TKw.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.402941\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233756cn4uZUvrFzdwhHef.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.463235\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Gilmour by Sahil Thappa</h3><p>来自印度的 <a href=\"https://ekprayogblog.wordpress.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sahil Thappa</a> 是一个名副其实的手工爱好者，受到叔叔亲手制作音响的启发，他推出了便携式音响 <a href=\"https://ekprayogblog.wordpress.com/tag/sonic-architect/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sonic Architect</a> 系列。在制作时，Thappa 尽量使用来自当地的材料以及组件，这款名为 Gilmour 的音响是他的最新作品，由皮革和木料手工打造的机箱带给人一种自然而亲切的感觉。你可以通过<a href=\"https://ekprayogblog.wordpress.com/2016/05/11/sonic-architect-gilmour/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>中的邮箱地址与 Thappa 交流订购事宜。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233700yFJ2X9ElktzIP0iM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233701BckdHzr3IZEMu7tN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233701qrOEQp4oxVNL9f28.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233701t9u5S7rzPsOja83E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233701XSfFYxWH2a4tQzie.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608162337013whStjNOzbxMy9VQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Wooden by Pum by Estudio Pum</h3><p>这组名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/41348409/Wooden-by-Pum\" rel=\"nofollow\">Wooden by Pum</a> 的木质玩具由巴西圣保罗的 Estudio Pum 工作室设计制作，曾在今年一月的 <a href=\"http://www.feiraplana.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Feira Plana</a> 书展上展出。设计师 Felipe Malaria 和 Javier Cifre 将形状各异的木块组合在一起，同时还在顶端打上了像是眼睛一样的小孔，令这些奇妙的角色看起来更活泼可爱。除了用作玩具之外，还有乐队将它们打造成小摇铃进行<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/maguaryo/mas-o-menos-bien-melody\" rel=\"nofollow\">配乐</a>。Wooden by Pum 不久后就会开始销售，如果有兴趣的话可以留意下 Estudio Pum 的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/estudiopum\" rel=\"nofollow\">网店</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233625RjzLZK25UVSHmFCa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.482857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233626SPkEr9m4HQl5hozA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.557500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233627sKj57CQpidyBqFzA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.566667\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608162336285HD9cIPd8LybCmfJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.611429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233631pPOZCo96eglviVY5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.574286\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Scales Rug by Producks</h3><p>这张名为 <a href=\"http://www.pro-ducks.com/#/scales-rug/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Scales Rug</a> 的地毯由 <a href=\"http://www.pro-ducks.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Producks</a> 工作室与手织地毯品牌 <a href=\"http://www.jaipurrugsco.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jaipur Rugs</a> 联手打造，设计师耗时两年研发出了一种全新的制作方法，并且在探索新式工艺的同时保留了传统美学的元素。远远看去，Scales Rug 和传统的东方式地毯并没有什么区别，凑近后你才会发现它其实由层层叠叠的羊毛毡组合而成，像是深海巨兽脱落的鳞片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233558OavwQbDCYZP9NHl1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608162335590N6fRE7F4P213hiW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233601Gmy46OQeonK3Y1u8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233601Cmf8NyMpdXTH50cs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>OLLLY Desk by Pavel Vetrov</h3><p>由 Pavel Vetrov （我们之前介绍过他设计的一款<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/31034.html\">极简书架</a>）设计的这张 OLLLY 实木桌是去年红点设计大奖的获奖作品，方正利落的外形适用于各种室内环境。Vetrov 在 OLLLY 的桌面上还设计了对称的凹槽，可以用来放置手机或是其他小物，可以满足人们日常使用需求。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608162335382zKfckWRv1VuaBS6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233538bBeT9Z6DQ50Actdz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233539QAy4dgvHBUqZM71i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816233539WBcvXo9N2G4pEzyS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608162335404kFltHML9JfnWw8E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608162335405Ayh03P9r1KLfk4s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}